OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy in
OL,6,Fthe northwest with some showery rain
OL,7,Fovernight. Otherwise a dry night
OL,8,Felsewhere with clear periods. Strong
OL,9,Fsouthwesterly winds in the northwest
OL,10,Fgradually easing down.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FSome bright or sunny spells
OL,13,Fwith a few showers in the west.
OL,14,FStaying largely dry across the east.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FPatchy
OL,17,Frain on Tuesday morning, a few heavy
OL,18,Fand slow moving showers breaking out
OL,19,Fin the afternoon. A few afternoon
OL,20,Fshowers on Wednesday. Rain followed by
OL,21,Fshowers on Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
